# Vlnplot
# Reverse Identity class back to the original status
Idents.name <- as.character(0:12)
names(Idents.name) <- c("PT-S1","PT-S2","PT-S3",
                        "LOH","TAL","DT&CD",
                        "Endo","SMC","MC","Podo",
                        "Fib","temp1","temp2")
